DOGECOIN (CRYPTO)

What is Dogecoin? 💰

Dogecoin is a cryptocurrency that started as a joke in 2013, featuring the popular Shiba Inu dog from the "Doge" meme. Despite its playful origins, Dogecoin has gained a huge following and is now one of the top cryptocurrencies!
